Ken Broskey has been diagnosed with stage 4 cancer . 
  He has taken a job as an Uber driver so he can pay off his mortgage so his daughter and grandchildren can live in his house . 
  Doctors have urged him to check into hospice care . 
  A college student has started a GoFundMe page for the man which has almost reached its $95,000 goal  . 
  Uber has donated $5,000 to the man and is donating $1 to a campaign for him . 
 